-我其实只想修剪一下。
- (woman) Roberta, the look is you.
- I just really wanted a trim.

15
00:01:41,781 --> 00:01:43,038
不行，这是你的生日礼物。
No, this is your birthday present.

16
00:01:43,050 --> 00:01:43,929
