99
00:07:51,406 --> 00:07:55,783
-我们节假日不休息。
-加里，进来吧。
- We're open seven days a week.
- Hey, Gary. Come on in!

100
00:08:01,666 --> 00:08:06,707
在加里的绿洲，你会梦想成真。
(TV) At Gary's Oasis
all your fantasizes can come true!

101
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:11,880
非常好。
(woman) Very good!

102
