It won't ever come back.

105
00:10:22,391 --> 00:10:25,060
当我告诉你丽贝塔时我已经杀了她
I killed that
when I told you about Rebecca.

106
00:10:25,186 --> 00:10:28,769
你可以在床上带着耳机看。
You can watch in the bedroom
with the headphones.

107
00:10:28,897 --> 00:10:30,937
我知道。
I know.

108
00:10:31,651 --> 00:10:33,026
加里，
Gary,...

109
00:10:33,152 --> 00:10:36,153
你是一直记得你的梦想吗？
...do you ever remember your dreams?

110
00:10:36,279 --> 00:10:38,319
不知道，我从来没想过
I dunno, I never thought about it.

111
00:10:38,448 --> 00:10:40,820
他们喜欢那个广告，你觉得呢？
They liked the commercial,
don't you think?

112
00:10:40,951 --> 00:10:43,407
每个人都觉得你很棒。
Everyone thought you were great.

113
00:10:44,705 --> 00:10:46,448
哦，你明天要…
Oh, you're gonna...

114
00:10:46,581 --> 00:10:49,748
…修理我汽车的收音机，是吗？
...pick up the radio for the car
for me tomorrow, aren't you?

115
00:10:49,876 --> 00:10:51,287
是。
Sure.

116
00:10:51,419 --> 00:10:53,459
哦，别忘了…
Oh, don't forget...

117
00:10:53,588 --> 00:10:59,461
告诉伙计你是我妻子，因为我们
在物主房间里放了一个烫发器
Tell the guy you're my wife because we
put a sauna in the owner's apartment...

118
00:10:59,594 --> 00:11:02,167
他会给我们一个好价钱。
...and he's giving us a really great price.

