Come on, let's just get outta here.

142
00:13:05,250 --> 00:13:08,700
-我必须去做那只消失的蓝鸟。
-听起来不错。
- I have to do the Disappearing Bluebird.
- Sounds great.

143
00:13:08,728 --> 00:13:10,767
