The band got this gig in Buffalo
and we start tonight.

169
00:16:31,682 --> 00:16:34,007
下次别在报纸上登广告了，行吗？
Next time don't put
an ad in the paper, OK?

170
00:16:34,142 --> 00:16:37,309
苏珊，我每周都在找你。
Susan, I've been looking for you
for weeks!

171
00:16:37,337 --> 00:16:39,330
陪我去Buffalo吧？
Come to Buffalo with me?

172
00:16:39,340 --> 00:16:41,297
嗯，你可是在工作。
uh-uh, you'll be working.

173
00:16:41,322 --> 00:16:43,778
-无聊的工作
-陪我去吧。
- (Susan) It's boring.
- Come to Buffalo.

174
00:16:43,809 --> 00:16:47,141
我不会让你闲着无聊的。
(Jim) I'll find some trouble
for you to get into.

175
00:16:47,270 --> 00:16:49,310
我现在已经没闲心了。
I've had enough trouble already.

176
00:16:52,609 --> 00:16:54,601
你…你和这人睡过？
You... you were with this guy?

177
00:16:54,735 --> 00:16:56,693
我离开时他还活着。
He was breathing when I left.

178
00:16:56,821 --> 00:17:00,771
嗨，你们美女和野兽两位，
我可不想在桥上出事，快走！
Hey! Beauty and the Beast,
we'll hit traffic on the bridge. Let's fly!

179
00:17:00,908 --> 00:17:02,533
《生之欲》
(# "Lust For Life" by lggy Pop on radio)

180
00:17:02,660 --> 00:17:04,699
我不能就这样离开你。
I don't like leaving you like this.

181
00:17:04,828 --> 00:17:08,364
-我能照顾好自己。
-好吧。
- I can take care of myself.
- I know.

182
00:17:08,499 --> 00:17:11,037
这样，我给你一个电话…
Look, I'll give you a number. uh...

183
00:17:11,835 --> 00:17:13,875
有笔吗？
You got a pen?

184
00:17:15,422 --> 00:17:18,542
好了，这是我朋友迪兹的电话。
All right, this is the number
of my friend Dez.

185
00:17:18,676 --> 00:17:20,714
他人不错…
He's a great guy...

186
00:17:20,844 --> 00:17:24,712
…如果你有困难了就打给他，他知道怎么联系我。
...and if you really get in a jam, call him.
He'll know how to reach me.

187
00:17:24,848 --> 00:17:28,762
-他有钱吗？
-别想了，他知道你是什么人。
- Has he got any money?
- Forget it! He knows all about you.

188
00:17:29,772 --> 00:17:32,856
Johnny Yen又来了，
# Here comes Johnny Yen again

189
00:17:33,733 --> 00:17:35,892
带着酒和毒品，
# With the liquor and drugs

190
00:17:36,028 --> 00:17:38,234
还有绞肉机
# And the flesh machine

191
00:17:38,363 --> 00:17:40,403
别寻刺激了，好吗？
No more dead bodies, OK?

192
00:17:40,532 --> 00:17:42,571
我要看看我能干出什么来。
I'll see what I can do.

193
00:17:43,493 --> 00:17:45,818
下次我回来还在这里见面。
Be here next time when I get back.

194
00:17:48,456 --> 00:17:53,118
自从上当后我就没有好转…
# And I been hurtin'
since I bought the gimmick...

195
00:18:27,077 --> 00:18:29,117
来吧，宝贝！
Come on, baby!

196
00:18:29,245 --> 00:18:31,737
注意看啊！
(vendor) Check it out!

197
00:18:35,961 --> 00:18:39,495
嗨，宝贝，这太阳镜专为你准备的。
Hey, baby, I got
a pair of sunglasses just for you!

198
00:18:41,466 --> 00:18:43,506
这帽子再适合你不过了。
This hat'll look great on you, baby.

199
00:18:43,635 --> 00:18:46,126
照照镜子，好看吧？
Take a look in the mirror.
Beautiful, right?

200
00:18:46,262 --> 00:18:48,385
十美元，便宜吧，十美元。
$10 for the set, all right? Ten bucks.

201
00:18:50,224 --> 00:18:52,513
你买吗？你哪里走？
You gonna buy?
Hey, where you goin', babe?

202
00:18:52,644 --> 00:18:55,134
站住！你拿了我的帽子知道吗？
Yo! Come back!
What are you doin' with my hat?

203
00:18:55,271 --> 00:18:57,678
还给我眼镜，怎么回事啊？
Give me my glasses, babe!
What's the matter?

204
00:18:57,815 --> 00:19:00,140
-哦，天，怎么会这样！
-对不起。
- Oh, man! I don't believe it!
- I'm sorry.

205
00:19:00,275 --> 00:19:02,315
你在干什么？
What are you doin'?

206
00:19:02,445 --> 00:19:04,816
-对不起。
-说句对不起就完了？
- I'm sorry.
- What do you mean, "sorry"? Hey!

207
00:19:04,947 --> 00:19:06,192
抱歉！
Sorry!

208
00:19:25,928 --> 00:19:29,427
《尊严》
(# "Respect" by Aretha Franklin
playing in shop)

209
00:19:49,204 --> 00:19:51,031
我不想继续你的错误
# I ain't gonna do you wrong

210
00:19:51,497 --> 00:19:53,490
当你离开
# While you're gone

211
00:19:53,625 --> 00:19:55,665
我不想继续你的错误
# Ain't gonna do you wrong

212
00:19:56,252 --> 00:19:57,746
因为我不想
# Cos I don't wanna

213
00:19:57,879 --> 00:19:59,670
就是你回家时当我问起…
# All I'm askin'

214
00:19:59,798 --> 00:20:02,752
…那一点点尊严
# Is for a little respect
when you come home

215
00:20:02,884 --> 00:20:05,636
亲爱的，当你回家
# Baby, when you get home

216
00:20:09,306 --> 00:20:11,549
我考虑给你
# I'm about to give you

217
00:20:11,975 --> 00:20:14,218
所有的钱
# All of my money

218
00:20:14,353 --> 00:20:16,429
# And all I'm askin'...

219
00:20:16,563 --> 00:20:19,350
给我个面子吧，不要穿出去。
Do me a favour, baby.
Stay on the carpet, OK?

220
00:20:19,483 --> 00:20:22,021
-挺好看的，是吧？
-是。
- They're great, aren't they?
- I know.

221
00:20:22,736 --> 00:20:24,776
我想要了，但是65美元的价钱有点…
I gotta have 'em, but 65 bucks...

222
00:20:24,905 --> 00:20:27,028
-那是定价。
-别管定价。
- That is the price.
- Forget it.

223
00:20:27,157 --> 00:20:30,942
-我喜欢你这夹克。
-这是Jimi Hendrix（摇滚明星）的。
- I like the jacket.
- It used to belong to Jimi Hendrix.

224
00:20:31,077 --> 00:20:34,660
但我愿意用夹克来换靴子。
But I bet he'd love it
if I swapped it for the boots.

225
00:20:35,540 --> 00:20:37,580
成交。
Deal.

226
00:20:46,426 --> 00:20:48,633
# Ooo, your kiss is

227
00:20:48,761 --> 00:20:50,255
# Sweeter than honey

228
00:20:52,014 --> 00:20:53,046
# And guess what?

229
00:20:53,182 --> 00:20:55,424
# So is my money...

230
00:21:05,779 --> 00:21:07,606
很招人喜欢，是吧？
Gorgeous, isn't it?

231
00:21:07,740 --> 00:21:09,780
它曾经可是猫王的。
It used to belong to Elvis Presley.

232
00:21:09,909 --> 00:21:12,578
-试一试吗？
-行。
- Wanna try it on?
- All right.

233
00:21:13,495 --> 00:21:15,821
# Oh, a little respect

234
00:21:17,708 --> 00:21:19,867
# Oh, hey! A little respect...

235
00:21:51,579 --> 00:21:53,820
我们从鸡蛋开始
(TV) We start off with the eggs.

236
00:21:54,749 --> 00:21:56,788
两个两个打，动作要快
These go very fast done two by two.

237
00:21:56,917 --> 00:21:58,957
你可以在早晨做
And this you can do in the morning...

238
00:21:59,878 --> 00:22:02,168
然后准备开始做菜。
...and get it all ready for baking.

239
00:22:02,298 --> 00:22:05,003
我会用新方法来做。
I'm gonna bake it and then unmould it.

240
00:22:06,218 --> 00:22:08,258
这有六个鸡蛋了。
There are your six eggs.

241
00:22:10,389 --> 00:22:14,517
然后用打蛋器搅拌…
Those get beaten up a little bit
and then in goes...

242
00:22:14,643 --> 00:22:16,600
嗨，罗伯塔
Hello, Roberta.

243
00:22:16,729 --> 00:22:18,685
嗨，朱莉娅
Hello, Julia.

244
00:22:18,813 --> 00:22:21,270
抱歉，主妇们，我不能在家吃晚饭。
Sorry, girls. I can't stay for dinner.

245
00:22:21,400 --> 00:22:24,187
西德的人订了1500个浴盆
Some guy from West Germany's
got 1500 tubs...

246
00:22:24,319 --> 00:22:26,311
他为人传统
...he can't get through customs.

247
00:22:26,446 --> 00:22:28,486
我得在镇上陪他吃饭。
I gotta go have dinner with him in town.

248
00:22:28,615 --> 00:22:31,188
就这一次，我抱歉，你能理解吗？
It just happened.
I'm sorry. You forgive me?

249
00:22:33,370 --> 00:22:35,409
看起来挺有意思的。
Looks interesting too.

250
00:22:36,290 --> 00:22:39,207
-选好了收音机了吗？
-收音机？
- Get a good deal on the radio?
- Radio?

251
00:22:39,333 --> 00:22:43,118
-汽车上的。你去城里干嘛去了？
-哦，对了，收音机。
- Car radio. You just came from the city.
- Oh, my God, the radio.

252
00:22:44,088 --> 00:22:46,128
-你忘了？
-不是。
- You forgot the radio?
- No!

253
00:22:46,841 --> 00:22:48,880
嗯，对，是，我忘了。
um... Yeah, right, I guess I did.

254
00:22:49,010 --> 00:22:52,011
你可以说你不吃晚饭了，而我却忙的不可开交。
You could have said
you didn't want dinner. I had to rush!

255
00:22:52,138 --> 00:22:54,130
你忙什么了？你说你什么地方都没去。
You said you didn't go anywhere.

256
00:22:54,264 --> 00:22:56,056
你穿的是什么？
What are you wearing?

257
00:22:57,142 --> 00:23:00,392
夹克。曾经是Jimi Hendrix的夹克。
A jacket.
It used to belong to Jimi Hendrix.

258
00:23:01,980 --> 00:23:04,305
你买了一个穿过的夹克？
怎么，我们是穷人吗？
You bought a used jacket?
What, are we poor?

259
00:23:04,441 --> 00:23:06,481
你这是怎么啦？
What's going on here?

260
00:23:12,449 --> 00:23:14,821
罗伯塔，我必须要去了。
Roberta, I gotta run! I'm late.

261
00:23:14,951 --> 00:23:17,110
我们晚些再谈吧。
We'll talk later, all right?

262
00:23:17,246 --> 00:23:19,451
晚些谈。
All right, we'll talk later?

263
00:23:23,501 --> 00:23:25,541
Jimi Hendrix,是吗？
Jimi Hendrix, huh?

264
00:23:35,096 --> 00:23:37,135
落地声
(clattering)

265
00:23:44,104 --> 00:23:46,144
电视声
(TV continues)

266
00:23:52,143 --> 00:23:54,078
警方寻找神秘女人

267
00:24:15,388 --> 00:24:17,428
你卖了？
You sold it?

268
00:24:18,391 --> 00:24:21,760
我落下了开储物柜的钥匙！
I had a key that was important.
I got my shit inside a locker.

269
00:24:21,895 --> 00:24:25,429
-我卖了。
-我留下名字和电话。
- I sold it!
- I'll leave you my name and number.

270
00:24:49,758 --> 00:24:51,797
动作好快，陌生人！
Good goin', stranger.

271
00:24:52,927 --> 00:24:54,966
什么他妈的陌生人？
Well, what fuckin' stranger?!

272
00:24:55,096 --> 00:24:57,966
大型通铺。这意味着尿裤子。
Festival seating. That means Portosans.

273
00:24:58,099 --> 00:25:02,428
尿裤子就是站着撒尿，我不想站着撒尿。
Portosans means pissing with flies.
I'm not gonna piss with flies.

274
00:25:02,561 --> 00:25:06,097
你们男人可以尿在瓶子里。
这算什么？木房子？
You guys can piss in bottles.
What the hell is this? Woodstock?

275
00:25:24,332 --> 00:25:26,372
电话声
(phone rings)

276
00:25:29,754 --> 00:25:31,996
-放映员
-迪兹，是我，吉姆。
- Projection.
- Dez, it's me. Jim.

277
00:25:32,132 --> 00:25:33,959
等一会儿。
Hold on a second.

278
00:25:34,928 --> 00:25:36,967
哦，我的天啊。
Jesus Christ!

279
00:25:37,097 --> 00:25:41,046
我在Buffalo脱不了身，请你帮个忙，
是关于苏珊的。
I'm stuck in Buffalo and I need a favour.
It's about Susan.

280
00:25:41,184 --> 00:25:46,973
是这样，她在大西洋城遇到的一个家伙
被人从旅店的窗户上扔了出去。
See, now some guy she met in Atlantic
City got pushed out of a hotel window.

281
00:25:47,106 --> 00:25:49,348
这里太乱了，我没听见。
This sounds wild. I'm sorry I missed it.

282
00:25:49,484 --> 00:25:51,523
迪兹，我没开玩笑。
This is serious, Dez.

283
00:25:51,652 --> 00:25:56,065
现在，一个署名陌生人的家伙登出启事
要在巴特利公园见她
And now some guy's run an ad to meet
her in Battery Park, signed "a stranger".

284
00:25:56,198 --> 00:26:00,326
这有点怪了，你能不能
It sounds weird.
Could you just go down there...

285
00:26:00,453 --> 00:26:02,326
去看一下她安全吗？
...and make sure she's OK?

286
00:26:02,455 --> 00:26:06,452
吉姆，维多利亚昨晚刚甩了我，
我心情糟透了。
Jim, Victoria split on me last night.
I'm in a shitty mood.

287
00:26:06,584 --> 00:26:09,454
我没法立刻就变成你的童子军。
I'm not in the mood for being a boy scout
right now.

288
00:26:09,587 --> 00:26:11,828
拜托了，迪兹，就耽误你半个小时。
Come on, Dez.
It'll take you half an hour.

289
00:26:11,963 --> 00:26:15,547
-好了没有？
-马上就好，一秒钟就好。
- (man) Come on!
- Give me a chance here. One second.

290
00:26:15,676 --> 00:26:17,254
起哄声
(booing)

291
00:26:17,386 --> 00:26:21,086
-她在四点去见他。
-四点？那可要差不多一个小时！
- She's got to meet him at 4 o'clock.
- That's in less than an hour!

292
00:26:21,223 --> 00:26:23,430
吉姆，我可是有工作的人！
Jim, I got a job here, you know!

293
00:26:23,558 --> 00:26:25,598
我求你了。
This one favour.

294
00:26:25,727 --> 00:26:28,182
即使我能找到人替我
Even if I could get someone
to fill in for me,...

295
00:26:28,313 --> 00:26:30,472
可我连她长得什么样都不知道。
...I don't even know what she looks like.

296
00:26:30,607 --> 00:26:32,646
听着，你不会找不到她的。
Look, you can't miss her.

297
00:26:32,775 --> 00:26:36,359
她很好看，金发，还有，中等身材
She's incredibly pretty,
blonde hair, uh... medium height.

298
00:26:36,488 --> 00:26:38,860
还有她穿着绿色的，上面画着金色的…
And she's got this green and gold jacket...

299
00:26:38,990 --> 00:26:43,237
一个锥形，一只眼睛在上面，就像钞票上那样。
（共济会标志）你肯定能找到她。
...with a pyramid with an eye on top
like a dollar bill. You can't miss it.

300
00:26:43,369 --> 00:26:47,616
-好吧，你要请我吃饭啊。
-行，多谢，我一定请你。
- All right, you owe me one.
- Great. Thanks, Dez, I appreciate it.

301
00:26:47,748 --> 00:26:47,988
好的，再见。
OK, yeah. Bye.

302
00:26:48,002 --> 00:26:50,041
我一辈子都在纽约。
I lived in New York all my life.

303
00:26:50,170 --> 00:26:53,337
我们老去中餐馆，意餐馆
We used to have Chinese restaurants,
ltalian restaurants.

304
00:26:53,465 --> 00:26:56,834
现在你去吃寿司。所有人都吃寿司。
Now you have these sushi restaurants.
Everyone goes for sushi.

305
00:26:56,969 --> 00:26:59,008
寿司，我讨厌这东西。
Sushi... I hate the stuff.

306
00:26:59,137 --> 00:27:01,889
我跟你说，尽管我有一天我买了一些，
Although, I tell you,
I had some the other day.

307
00:27:02,015 --> 00:27:05,764
回家做了，还不错的，味道像鱼。
I took it home, I cooked it, it wasn't bad.
It tasted like fish.

308
00:27:05,894 --> 00:27:07,933
鼓声
(drumming)

309
00:27:30,711 --> 00:27:32,751
9块2.
$9.20.

310
00:27:35,049 --> 00:27:37,089
给，不用找了。
Here, keep the change.

311
00:27:37,218 --> 00:27:40,385
哇，这是什么？嗨，女士！
Whoa! Hey! What is that? Hey, lady!

312
00:27:40,513 --> 00:27:42,552
嗨，女士！
Hey! Hey, lady!

313
00:27:42,681 --> 00:27:44,639
这算什么？
What is this?

314
00:27:44,767 --> 00:27:46,676
靠，刁民！
Oh, that's cute!

315
00:27:51,398 --> 00:27:53,438
嗨
Hi.

316
00:27:55,486 --> 00:27:58,107
我以前好像见过你。
You look like I've seen you
somewhere before.

317
00:27:58,239 --> 00:28:01,109
-不，我想不是。
-我想是。
- No, I don't think so.
- Yeah, I think so.

318
00:28:03,618 --> 00:28:07,366
-你现在在做什么事情吗？
-我在等人。
- You doin' anything right now?
- I'm waiting for someone.

319
00:28:18,091 --> 00:28:21,294
-跟我走，小姐。
-你不明白，我必须去见一个人。
- Come with me, miss.
- I have to meet someone.

320
00:28:21,427 --> 00:28:24,381
-我们谈谈出租车里的事情。
-她那里有我所有的东西。
- We'll talk about it in the car.
- She's got all my stuff.

321
00:28:24,514 --> 00:28:27,265
她会给你他妈的打车费。
She'll give you the goddamn cab fare!

322
00:28:28,601 --> 00:28:32,301
我也不想这样，可我也得生活。
(driver) I don't need this aggravation.
I work for a living.

323
00:28:32,438 --> 00:28:34,477
想吃霸王餐，我知道法律。
Theft of services. I know the law.

324
00:28:35,733 --> 00:28:39,268
嗨，打扰了，你喜欢吃糖吗？
Well, hi!
Excuse me, but do you like candy?

325
00:28:39,403 --> 00:28:42,155
-我这有甜甜糖。
-不，谢谢。
- I got some Sugar Babies.
- No, thank you.

326
00:28:42,281 --> 00:28:46,908
我久想谈一谈，我认识你在大西洋城的的男朋友。
I wanted to have a chat. I was very close
to your boyfriend in Atlantic City.

327
00:28:47,035 --> 00:28:51,033
-不可能，我结婚了。
-我不这样想。
- No, no, no. I'm married.
- No, I don't think so!

328
00:28:54,753 --> 00:28:56,164
苏珊？
Susan!

329
00:28:56,297 --> 00:28:58,621
你有一对他给你的漂亮的耳环吗？
Did you wear the pretty earrings
he gave you?

330
00:28:58,757 --> 00:29:02,458
-我们得谈谈，我的车就在附近。
-放开我！
- Let's have a chat. My car is over there.
- Let go of me!

331
00:29:02,595 --> 00:29:05,382
