他担心坏了。
He was pretty worried.

502
00:41:57,877 --> 00:41:59,917
摔了？
Killed?

503
00:42:00,046 --> 00:42:01,920
杀死了？
Dead?

504
00:42:02,048 --> 00:42:05,631
这也是你的兴趣之一，是吗，苏珊？
Sort of goes with the territory,
doesn't it, Susan?

505
00:42:08,096 --> 00:42:10,136
也许我知道是谁干的。
Maybe I know who did it.

506
00:42:11,807 --> 00:42:13,847
我希望我能想起来。
I wish I could remember.

507
00:42:15,062 --> 00:42:17,101
也许就是你杀的。
Maybe you were the killer.

508
00:42:17,940 --> 00:42:19,979
不可能。
No! (laughs)

509
00:42:25,322 --> 00:42:28,276
我想我要躺一会儿
I should probably lay low for while, huh?

510
00:42:28,867 --> 00:42:30,906
好主意。
It might be a wise idea.

511
00:42:32,704 --> 00:42:35,658
你不知道在码头的那个人是谁？
You don't know
who the guy at the quay was?

512
00:42:38,209 --> 00:42:40,248
也许是被你抛弃的情人
Maybe a jilted lover?

513
00:42:41,965 --> 00:42:44,005
肯定不是。
I don't think so.

514
00:42:46,845 --> 00:42:48,884
也有可能。
Maybe he was.

515
00:42:49,764 --> 00:42:51,887
你可知道
You know somethin'?

516
00:42:52,016 --> 00:42:54,637
你不完全是我所想的那样。
You are not at all what I expected.

517
00:42:56,187 --> 00:42:58,725
你也不全是我想的那样。
You're not quite what I expected either.

518
00:43:00,774 --> 00:43:02,814
萨克斯
(sax ophone)

519
00:43:20,168 --> 00:43:23,205
我怎么认识的吉姆？我是说…
Just how did I meet Jim? I mean, how...

520
00:43:23,963 --> 00:43:26,003
我怎么遇到他的？
How did I meet him?

521
00:43:26,133 --> 00:43:28,171
也许这个有帮助。
Maybe it would help.

522
00:43:28,301 --> 00:43:30,757
我想是在那个咖啡店里。
I think it was at some coffee shop.

523
00:43:32,055 --> 00:43:34,094
那是你工作的第一天，
It was your first day at work.

524
00:43:34,223 --> 00:43:36,263
吉姆大摇大摆的进来。
Jim waltzed in.

525
00:43:36,392 --> 00:43:39,177
你给他带来吃的，然后把帐单撕了。
You brought his food over
and you ripped up the check.

526
00:43:39,189 --> 00:43:42,474
他个高吗？我说的是吉姆。
Is he tall? I mean Jim.

527
00:43:43,485 --> 00:43:45,726
中等个头吧。
He's about medium.

528
00:43:47,238 --> 00:43:49,278
哪种身材？
Is he sort of thin?

529
00:43:50,700 --> 00:43:52,739
哪种，哪种，呃…
Sort of. Sort of, um...

530
00:43:53,661 --> 00:43:55,653
跟我差不多。
...my build.

531
00:43:59,333 --> 00:44:01,456
眼睛是什么颜色的？
What colour eyes does he have?

532
00:44:05,673 --> 00:44:07,581
蓝的。
Blue.

533
00:44:07,716 --> 00:44:09,756
跟你一样？
Like yours?

534
00:44:15,641 --> 00:44:17,634
抱歉，抱歉。
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

535
00:44:17,769 --> 00:44:19,808
抱歉。
(Roberta whispers) Sorry.

536
00:44:21,188 --> 00:44:23,894
我不知道怎么回事，只是…
I don't know what happened. I just...

537
00:44:24,692 --> 00:44:26,186
不好意思。
Sorry.

538
00:44:30,781 --> 00:44:32,820
雷声
(thunder rumbles)

539
00:45:28,299 --> 00:45:30,339
哼哼
(groans)

540
00:45:38,267 --> 00:45:40,307
过来。
Come on.

541
00:46:02,541 --> 00:46:04,580
迪兹
(whispers) Dez!

542
00:46:05,419 --> 00:46:07,457
迪兹
Dez...

543
00:46:10,968 --> 00:46:13,007
和我一起吃早餐吗？
Wanna go out to breakfast with me?

544
00:46:13,971 --> 00:46:16,010
早餐
Breakfast?

545
00:46:18,225 --> 00:46:21,142
你怎么了？穿的有点恶心。
What have you got on?
Some sort of disguise?

546
00:46:21,269 --> 00:46:24,519
-你不喜欢？
-不，只是，呃…
- You don't like it?
- No, it's, uh...

547
00:46:24,647 --> 00:46:27,434
还是迷人的。
...sort of charming.

548
00:46:28,777 --> 00:46:30,519
我请客。
It's my treat.

549
00:46:31,696 --> 00:46:33,735
你要干嘛？抢银行？
What did you do? Rob a bank?

550
00:46:33,864 --> 00:46:36,782
我不知道，也许吧。
I don't know. Maybe.

551
00:46:38,536 --> 00:46:40,410
你要到哪里去？
Where do you wanna go?

552
00:46:40,537 --> 00:46:42,779
看，我在手提箱找到这个。
See, I found this in the suitcase.

553
00:46:44,375 --> 00:46:46,415
Gunny的咖啡店？我知道这地方。
Gunny's Coffee Shop? I know the place.

554
00:46:46,543 --> 00:46:48,583
它在中央大街附近。
It's over on Center Street.

555
00:46:48,712 --> 00:46:51,499
也许我就是在那儿遇见吉姆的。
Maybe that's the place where I met Jim.

556
00:46:52,091 --> 00:46:53,419
-然后？
-然后…
- So?
- So...

557
00:46:53,551 --> 00:46:57,963
然后我们就去那里
看看是否有人认识我。
So we go there
and see if anybody remembers me.

558
00:46:58,097 --> 00:47:01,346
看得怎么样，有熟悉的吗？
So what do you think?
Anyone look familiar?

559
00:47:01,809 --> 00:47:04,051
还没有。
No. Not yet.

560
00:47:11,820 --> 00:47:14,655
我在手提箱里找到这个，你听说过吗？
I found this in the suitcase.
You ever hear of it?

561
00:47:14,781 --> 00:47:18,315
魔术俱乐部？是的，在百老汇附近。
The Magic Club? Yeah.
That's that place over on Broadway.

562
00:47:18,451 --> 00:47:19,779
怎么了？
Why?

563
00:47:19,911 --> 00:47:22,616
我想我应该去那，看看有没有熟人。
I thought I'd go there
and see if I remember anyone.

564
00:47:22,747 --> 00:47:25,452
-你知道你要点什么吗？
-当然。
- You know what you're having?
- Sure.

565
00:47:25,583 --> 00:47:27,623
你要点什么？
What are you having?

566
00:47:27,752 --> 00:47:29,792
嗯，是你请客，对吧？
Well, it's your treat, right?

567
00:47:29,921 --> 00:47:31,913
是的，我付账。
(giggles) Yeah, I got money.

568
00:47:32,048 --> 00:47:34,124
我要点…蓝莓点心。
I'm gonna have... blueberry blintzes.

569
00:47:34,259 --> 00:47:36,297
很好，我也要那个。
I'll have that too. That sounds good.

570
00:47:36,427 --> 00:47:38,467
你要点什么？
What can I get you?

571
00:47:38,596 --> 00:47:40,968
呃，一杯咖啡。
Yes, I would like a... coffee...

572
00:47:41,724 --> 00:47:44,096
还有…甜圈饼
...and a, uh... doughnut.

573
00:47:44,226 --> 00:47:48,473
小姐，如果你有空了，就给我们上吃的吧。
Miss! When you get a chance,
could you take our order?

574
00:47:48,606 --> 00:47:50,563
给你可以，她可不行。
You can stay. She's gotta go.

575
00:47:50,690 --> 00:47:53,229
Mick，那个穿夹克的疯子女孩来了。
Mick, it's that crazy girl with the jacket.

576
00:47:53,360 --> 00:47:55,399
-你，滚！
-你认识我？
- You, out!
- You know me?!

577
00:47:55,529 --> 00:47:57,652
对，别想在这儿吃霸王餐。
Yeah. You won't get a free meal here.

578
00:47:57,781 --> 00:48:01,150
-我有钱，我可以付款。
-我不要你的钱，滚出去。
- I got money, I can pay.
- I don't want your money. Get out.

579
00:48:01,284 --> 00:48:03,989
-我们有钱，怎么了？
-想想你自己的事吧。
- We got money. What is it?
- Mind your own business.

580
00:48:04,120 --> 00:48:06,872
-这就是我的事，等一下。
-过来，出去。
- This is my business, wait a minute!
- Come on, out!

581
00:48:06,998 --> 00:48:09,302
-嘿，我和他一起的。
-出去，出去。
- Hey, I'm with her.
- Come on, come on.

582
00:48:09,310 --> 00:48:11,683
你幸运去吧，我没向你逼帐！
You're lucky I don't press charges!

583
00:48:11,713 --> 00:48:13,338
迪兹。
Dez.

584
00:48:13,465 --> 00:48:16,038
你怎么样，还好吧？太对不起了。
Are you OK? Are you all right? I'm sorry!

585
00:48:16,176 --> 00:48:18,251
我说的第一条规则就是别给我找事。
Rule number one was no drama.

586
00:48:18,386 --> 00:48:21,553
-记得吗？
-是的，我知道，抱歉。
- Remember?
- Yes. I know. I'm sorry.

587
00:48:23,057 --> 00:48:24,849
我们走吧。
Let's get out of here.

588
00:48:24,976 --> 00:48:26,554
不好意思。
I'm sorry.

589
00:48:38,741 --> 00:48:40,818
争吵声
(man and woman arguing)

590
00:48:40,951 --> 00:48:43,987
你从来不让我戴眼镜。
(woman)
You won't even let me wear my glasses!

591
00:48:44,121 --> 00:48:47,537
回去卖T去吧，你被解雇了！
(man) Go back to selling T-shirts!
You're fired!

592
00:48:47,667 --> 00:48:50,833
不对，你错了，蓝，是我辞职不干了。
(shouts) No, you don't, lan, because I quit!

593
00:48:52,963 --> 00:48:55,502
嘿，别在梯子下面！
(Susan) Hey! Not under the ladder!

594
00:48:58,093 --> 00:49:02,221
我的命运绝不可能比这儿更糟糕的了。
败类人渣！
My luck can't get much worse anyway.
Miserable scumbags!

595
00:49:02,973 --> 00:49:05,429
也许我应该在床上教训他。
Maybe I should've slept with him.

596
00:49:04,559 --> 00:49:07,346
姐们，有个巫婆偷了我的衣服…
Man, some witch steals my clothes,...

597
00:49:07,479 --> 00:49:11,725
…米克尔被人从旅店窗户扔了出去，
现在你又被炒了。
...Meeker gets pushed out a hotel window
and now you get fired.

598
00:49:11,858 --> 00:49:16,151
不太糟，但是坏运气好像抓着你不放。
No offence, but bad luck really seems
to be following you around.

599
00:49:18,823 --> 00:49:22,156
我们现在都清闲了，一起去看个电影吧。
We're both free now.
Let's just go to the movies.

600
00:49:22,285 --> 00:49:24,323
两场连映的？
A double feature?

601
00:49:24,453 --> 00:49:26,493
来吧。
Come on!

602
00:49:28,498 --> 00:49:31,251
如果你请我吃爆米花的话，电影票就我买了。
I'll pay for the movie
if you pay for the popcorn.

603
00:49:31,377 --> 00:49:32,954
可以，但是，爆米花多少钱？
OK, but listen. How much is popcorn?

604
00:49:33,086 --> 00:49:35,126
-2.50
-行。
- 2.50
- OK.

605
00:49:37,216 --> 00:49:39,255
笑
(giggling)

606
00:49:46,225 --> 00:49:48,264
就是这地方。
This must be the place.

607
00:49:48,394 --> 00:49:51,311
司机，靠边停吧，就是这儿。
Sir, could you pull over, please?
This is it.

608
00:49:52,856 --> 00:49:54,896
真是不好意思。
I'm sorry about what happened.

609
00:49:55,692 --> 00:49:58,148
-你没有生气吧？
-没。
- Are you sure you're not angry?
- Yeah.

610
00:49:58,987 --> 00:50:01,027
-真的。
-我没生气。
- Really?
- I'm not angry.

611
00:50:01,823 --> 00:50:03,863
你真够哥们。
OK. You're a real pal.

612
00:50:05,285 --> 00:50:07,324
我会告诉吉姆的。
I'll tell Jim.

613
00:50:08,121 --> 00:50:10,031
-拜
-拜
- Bye!
- Bye.

614
00:50:15,256 --> 00:50:17,294
够哥们，我会告诉吉姆…
A real pal. I'll tell Jim...

615
00:50:20,009 --> 00:50:22,168
布利克大街电影院
Bleecker Street Cinema.

616
00:50:32,313 --> 00:50:34,768
你只是别再这样开除谁！
(man)
You just don't fire someone like that!

617
00:50:34,899 --> 00:50:36,975
我上哪里去找这么文静的女孩去？
Who am I gonna find
at such short notice?

618
00:50:37,110 --> 00:50:39,149
拜托，你认识那么多女孩。
Come on, Ray. You know lots of girls.

619
00:50:39,278 --> 00:50:43,193
-很多女人都在找工作。
-妈，别打扰我。
- (woman) Plenty of women need work.
- (Ray) Ma! Let me take care of this.

620
00:50:43,324 --> 00:50:44,403
你好。
Hello.

621
00:50:44,534 --> 00:50:46,407
你看见外边的招工告示了？
You saw the sign outside?

622
00:50:46,535 --> 00:50:48,444
你是在找工作？
Are you looking for a job?

623
00:50:49,248 --> 00:50:51,323
是的，我想我是。
Yeah. Yeah, I think I am.

624
00:50:51,457 --> 00:50:53,616
-她还在想她在找工作。
-不。
- She thinks she's looking for a job.
- No!

625
00:50:53,752 --> 00:50:56,373
我是在找工作，是什么工作？
I am, I am! What kind of job?

626
00:50:56,504 --> 00:50:58,627
进来吧。
Come on in.

627
00:50:58,756 --> 00:51:00,796
这位是雷。
This is Ray.

628
00:51:00,925 --> 00:51:02,964
-您好。
-这位是雷的妈妈，格蕾妲。
- Hello.
- This is Ray's mom, Gilda.

629
00:51:03,094 --> 00:51:04,209
嗨。
Hi.

630
00:51:04,346 --> 00:51:05,969
-这位是哈雷。
-嗨。
- This is Henry.
- Hi.

631
00:51:06,097 --> 00:51:07,472
您好，哈雷。
Hello, Henry.

632
00:51:07,598 --> 00:51:09,638
还有我，蓝。
And I'm lan.

633
00:51:12,103 --> 00:51:14,060
收音机
(radio on)

634
00:51:24,699 --> 00:51:26,737
加里先生，你还好吗？
Are you OK, Mr Glass?

635
00:51:26,867 --> 00:51:29,240
还行，谢谢你。晚安，Daisy。
Fine, thank you. Good night, Daisy.

636
00:51:29,370 --> 00:51:31,695
我希望加里夫人没事。
I hope you get good news
about Mrs Glass.

637
00:51:31,830 --> 00:51:32,826
谢谢。
Thank you.

638
00:51:33,415 --> 00:51:35,407
你拿这个包去哪？
Where did you get this bag?

639
00:51:35,542 --> 00:51:37,582
它是我的，加里夫人把它给我了。
It's mine. Mrs Glass give it to me.

640
00:51:37,711 --> 00:51:39,750
把包给我，Daisy。
Give me the bag, Daisy.

641
00:51:40,547 --> 00:51:43,797
-Daisy，把包给我。
-对不起，这包是我的。
- Daisy, give me the bag!
- Sorry, you ain't getting this bag.

642
00:51:43,926 --> 00:51:47,091
-请你给我，我要好好的问问你。
-这包是我的。
- Please, I'm asking you nicely.
- You're not getting this.

643
00:51:47,220 --> 00:51:49,676
《笨蛋主持》
(# "Sucker MCs" by Run DMC
on ghetto blaster)

644
00:51:56,607 --> 00:52:00,854
嘿，我说，你们能挪个地方吃东西吗？
Hey, guys. Could you, uh...
have your picnic somewhere else?

645
00:52:08,035 --> 00:52:10,075
嘿，你们这些人！
Hey, guys!

646
00:52:11,748 --> 00:52:13,123
好吧，
Right...

647
00:52:13,249 --> 00:52:15,704
小心轻放，行吧？
Just try to be careful, all right?

648
00:52:17,046 --> 00:52:20,297
听着，我不想卷入家庭纠纷，好吗。
Listen, I don't get involved
in domestic disputes, OK?

649
00:52:20,425 --> 00:52:22,251
不是纠纷。
There's no dispute.

650
00:52:22,385 --> 00:52:24,710
在她没有失踪前时，她穿着一件夹克。
She had the jacket on
when she disappeared.

651
00:52:24,846 --> 00:52:27,882
某种原因上讲，这对她很不一样。
It was very special to her
for some reason.

652
00:52:28,016 --> 00:52:30,091
你真的记不起来她了？
Don't you even remember her?

653
00:52:30,226 --> 00:52:32,266
你也记不起来夹克了？
Don't you remember the jacket?

654
00:52:32,395 --> 00:52:37,056
黑色的，上面还有一个金色的像金字塔的图形
It was black and gold and it had
a sort of a pyramid thing on it...

655
00:52:37,191 --> 00:52:38,934
就像钞票上的那样。
...like on a dollar bill.

656
00:52:39,068 --> 00:52:41,108
记不清了。
Vaguely.

657
00:52:41,237 --> 00:52:44,403
很好，谢谢，你可真会帮忙。
Great. Thanks.
You've been a terrific help.

658
00:52:44,531 --> 00:52:46,607
等等，等等。
Wait a minute, wait a minute.

659
00:52:47,367 --> 00:52:50,368
她也来过这儿找夹克。
She stopped in here
looking for the jacket, too.

660
00:52:50,495 --> 00:52:52,535
也许你们能互相帮助。
Maybe you can help each other.

661
00:52:52,664 --> 00:52:54,703
电话铃
(phone rings)

662
00:52:54,833 --> 00:52:56,873
苏珊，接一下电话。
Susan, will you get the phone?

663
00:52:57,002 --> 00:52:58,911
电话铃
(ringing continues)

664
00:52:59,045 --> 00:53:01,121
苏珊，电话！
Susan! The phone's ringing!

665
00:53:03,175 --> 00:53:05,214
苏珊！
Susan!

666
00:53:14,101 --> 00:53:16,141
你好。
Hello?

667
00:53:16,312 --> 00:53:18,637
等下，她在这儿。
Yeah, hold on. She's right here.

668
00:53:20,525 --> 00:53:23,859
-什么事？
-你的另一个暗恋者。
- What?
- Another one of your secret admirers.

669
00:53:23,987 --> 00:53:26,026
喂？
Hello?

670
00:53:26,531 --> 00:53:28,571
是，你是谁？
Yeah. Who is this?

671
00:53:30,326 --> 00:53:31,951
加里・格兰斯？
Gary Glass?

672
00:53:35,457 --> 00:53:37,497
嗯，嗯。
uh-huh.

673
00:53:37,626 --> 00:53:41,125
哦，你就是巫婆的丈夫，我的东西呢？
Oh, so you're the witch's husband.
Where's my stuff?

674
00:53:42,588 --> 00:53:44,415
嗯。
Yeah.

675
00:53:44,925 --> 00:53:46,751
嗯。
Yeah.

676
00:53:46,884 --> 00:53:48,924
嗯。也许我能帮你。
Well, maybe I could help you.

677
00:53:49,595 --> 00:53:54,672
听着，今晚10点30到西21世纪街30号去见我。
Listen, meet me tonight at 10.30
