我已经结婚四年了。
I've been married for four years.

1018
01:18:38,933 --> 01:18:40,592
我丈夫加里…
My husband Gary...

1019
01:18:40,725 --> 01:18:44,889
他做浴盆和浴室的生意。
He sells bathroom spas and saunas.

1020
01:18:50,235 --> 01:18:52,275
你怎么还是这样？
You never stop, do you?

1021
01:18:52,403 --> 01:18:54,610
不，这是真的，真的。
No, really! Really!

1022
01:18:54,739 --> 01:18:59,366
这就是我喜欢你的原因，我从不知道你
下一句会说什么，过来。
That's why I like you. I never know
what you'll say next. Come here.

1023
01:19:02,705 --> 01:19:05,659
-门锁声
-迪兹。
- (door lock rattles)
- Dez.

1024
01:19:08,378 --> 01:19:10,417
-那是什么？
-不知道。
- What is that?
- I dunno.

1025
01:19:12,757 --> 01:19:14,796
有人想进来。
Someone's trying to get in.

1026
01:19:24,976 --> 01:19:26,969
哦，天啊。
Oh, my God.

1027
01:19:27,104 --> 01:19:29,097
哦，是吉姆。
Oh, my God, it's Jim.

1028
01:19:29,230 --> 01:19:31,270
天啊。
Oh, my God.

1029
01:19:32,236 --> 01:19:35,771
吉姆，吉姆。
Jim... Jim. Jim.

1030
01:19:36,239 --> 01:19:41,281
谢天谢地，你吓坏我了。你觉得怎么样，啊？
Thank God. You had me worried.
How you doing, man? Huh? Huh?

1031
01:19:41,411 --> 01:19:44,282
有人打我了，一片黑。
Somebody jumped me. It was dark.

1032
01:19:44,998 --> 01:19:47,157
嗯，呃…
Yeah. uh...

1033
01:19:47,709 --> 01:19:49,748
是我干的。
It was me.

1034
01:19:50,504 --> 01:19:53,041
我以为你是别人呢。
I thought you were somebody else.

1035
01:19:53,173 --> 01:19:55,212
你以为我是谁？
Who did you think I was?

1036
01:19:56,801 --> 01:20:00,384
有人跟踪了苏珊，我想你可能是他。
Somebody's been following Susan.
I thought maybe you were him.

1037
01:20:00,513 --> 01:20:02,470
谁跟踪她？
Who's following her?

1038
01:20:02,598 --> 01:20:04,342
不知道。
I don't know.

1039
01:20:04,475 --> 01:20:06,267
你知道苏珊。
You know Susan.

1040
01:20:06,394 --> 01:20:09,845
从她那里得到一个清楚的答案真是困难。
It's really tough
to get a straight answer out of her.

1041
01:20:10,108 --> 01:20:12,101
她需要我，迪兹。
She needs me, Dez.

1042
01:20:12,234 --> 01:20:14,560
我想或许她准备安顿下来了。
I think maybe she's ready to settle down.

1043
01:20:14,696 --> 01:20:19,156
安顿下来？苏珊？别扯了，吉姆。
Settle down? Susan? Come on, Jim!

1044
01:20:19,284 --> 01:20:22,368
她从没有做过什么安顿的事，
她不是那类人。
She'd never do that.
She's really not the type.

1045
01:20:22,494 --> 01:20:24,487
从什么时候你这么了解她？
Since when do you know her so well?

1046
01:20:24,622 --> 01:20:28,701
呃，我只是不能看见她安顿下来。
我是说，她太野性了。
Well, I just can't see her settling down.
I mean, she's too wild.

1047
01:20:28,834 --> 01:20:31,160
但是这也是她的魅力。
But that's what's so great about her.

1048
01:20:31,294 --> 01:20:32,872
是这样吗？
Is that so?

1049
01:20:33,004 --> 01:20:36,338
我是说，你真的好像对她做了一番检查。
I mean, you really seem
to have examined this.

1050
01:20:37,051 --> 01:20:40,134
嗯，我们一起度过了一些时间。
Well, we've been spending
some time together.

1051
01:20:43,181 --> 01:20:45,933
可…你在说什么呀，迪兹？
Just... what are you saying here, Dez?

1052
01:20:46,059 --> 01:20:47,469
啊？
Huh?

1053
01:20:49,938 --> 01:20:52,179
我不想对你胡说八道，吉姆。
I'm not gonna bullshit you, Jim.

1054
01:20:52,315 --> 01:20:55,399
是一件不好出口的事，
我没说它没有。
It was a shitty thing to do.
I'm not saying it wasn't.

1055
01:20:56,485 --> 01:20:59,272
但是你自己说她诱人的。
But you yourself said she was irresistible.

1056
01:20:59,616 --> 01:21:01,655
哦，不会吧。
Oh, man.

1057
01:21:01,784 --> 01:21:05,284
你，你为什么不再打我一下，就像这样的，
把我结果了？
W-why don't you just hit me again
and, like, finish me off?

1058
01:21:05,413 --> 01:21:07,453
-你看…
-啊？
- Look...
- Huh?!

1059
01:21:07,581 --> 01:21:10,120
别哭喊了。我真的为她而疯狂…
Don't cry about it.
I'm really crazy about her...

1060
01:21:10,252 --> 01:21:12,243
…而且她也为我而疯狂。
...and she's really crazy about me.

1061
01:21:12,378 --> 01:21:14,704
-我对不起，
-听着，我了解苏珊。
- I'm sorry.
- Listen. I know Susan.

1062
01:21:14,838 --> 01:21:17,045
无论她告诉什么都是胡扯。
Whatever she told you doesn't mean shit.

1063
01:21:17,175 --> 01:21:21,338
她不是认真的，迪兹。我是知道的，
我追了她好几年了。
She plays with people, Dez. I oughta
know, I've been chasing her for years.

1064
01:21:21,470 --> 01:21:23,842
我认为她跟我是认真的。
I don't think she's playing with me.

1065
01:21:23,972 --> 01:21:26,012
胡说。
Bullshit.

1066
01:21:26,767 --> 01:21:28,641
这样吧，吉姆。
All right, Jim.

1067
01:21:28,769 --> 01:21:30,809
我们干嘛不问问她呢？
Why don't we just ask her?

1068
01:21:32,357 --> 01:21:33,768
苏珊。
Susan!

1069
01:21:33,900 --> 01:21:36,188
苏…她在这儿？
Su...! You mean she's here?!

1070
01:21:36,570 --> 01:21:37,981
苏珊。
Susan!

1071
01:21:38,113 --> 01:21:40,569
-到这儿来。
-苏珊。
- Come on out here.
- Susan...!

1072
01:21:44,161 --> 01:21:46,201
苏珊。
Susan!

1073
01:21:55,672 --> 01:21:57,712
她走了。
She's gone.

1074
01:21:59,635 --> 01:22:01,591
她就在这儿。
She was here.

1075
01:22:01,719 --> 01:22:03,759
我发誓。
I swear to God.

1076
01:22:03,889 --> 01:22:05,927
水壶鸣响
(kettle whistles)

1077
01:22:52,771 --> 01:22:54,811
迪兹，你在上面吗？
(Jim) Dez, are you up there?

1078
01:22:56,233 --> 01:22:57,893
怎么了？
Yeah?

1079
01:22:59,612 --> 01:23:02,696
猜猜怎么了？
我想她把我俩都耍了。
Guess what, man?
I think she's jerking us both around.

1080
01:23:02,824 --> 01:23:04,448
你什么意思？
What do you mean?

1081
01:23:04,574 --> 01:23:08,026
你看看吧，这个他妈的陌生人是谁？
Check this out.
I mean, who the hell is this stranger?

1082
01:23:08,162 --> 01:23:09,407
鼓
(drum roll)

1083
01:23:23,010 --> 01:23:25,679
苏珊，我还是不明白我们来这儿干什么。
Susan, I still don't understand
why we're here.

1084
01:23:25,804 --> 01:23:28,094
信我吧，加里。你会惊喜万分的。
Trust me, Gar.
You're in for a real surprise.

1085
01:23:28,224 --> 01:23:31,142
你的惊喜万分已经让我紧张了。
Your surprises are beginning
to make me nervous.

1086
01:23:31,269 --> 01:23:34,056
-她怎么说？
-我们会惊喜万分的。
- What'd she say?
- We're in for a real surprise.

1087
01:23:34,188 --> 01:23:36,643
我想我们在这儿看不到Tony Bennett。
I guess we're not gonna see
Tony Bennett here.

1088
01:23:36,774 --> 01:23:38,813
我应该叫警察跟着我们。
I'd settle for a police escort.

1089
01:23:38,942 --> 01:23:41,777
你怎么能让她穿上罗伯塔的夹克？
How could you let her wear
Roberta's jacket?

1090
01:23:41,903 --> 01:23:46,032
嘿，她没衣服了，总得穿点什么吧。
Hey, she's cold.
She's gotta wear something.

1091
01:23:46,157 --> 01:23:48,530
为什么你不把你的指甲剪了？
(dummy) Why don't you
cut your fingernails?

1092
01:23:48,660 --> 01:23:50,949
我听不见你在说啥…
I can't hear what you're saying...

1093
01:23:51,079 --> 01:23:53,119
捂住叫喊
(muffled shouting)

1094
01:23:56,628 --> 01:24:00,577
迪兹，如果她看到我们俩都在这儿，
她很可能又一走了之。
Dez, if she sees us both here,
she'll probably just split again.

1095
01:24:00,715 --> 01:24:02,754
那你回去吧。
You could go home.

1096
01:24:02,883 --> 01:24:05,837
我要看看他妈的陌生人是谁。
I wanna see who this fuckin' stranger is.

1097
01:24:12,935 --> 01:24:17,015
让我猜。三倍龙舌兰到天亮。
Let me guess. Triple tequila sunrise.

1098
01:24:17,147 --> 01:24:19,223
姜味汽水。
Ginger ale.

1099
01:24:22,026 --> 01:24:23,936
你是威士忌。
And you're the Scotch.

1100
01:24:24,070 --> 01:24:25,980
这是你的。
This must be yours.

1101
01:24:26,115 --> 01:24:28,153
朗姆酒和Tab。
Rum and Tab.

1102
01:24:31,704 --> 01:24:34,574
坐着别动，我去找找陌生人。
Sit tight. I'm gonna
go look for the stranger.

1103
01:24:35,541 --> 01:24:37,580
什么陌生人？
What stranger?

1104
01:24:37,710 --> 01:24:40,876
-天，她可真迷人。
-一坨漂亮的屎罢了。
- God, she's gorgeous.
- Beauty feces.

1105
01:24:53,975 --> 01:24:55,470
她在那。
There she is.

1106
01:24:55,602 --> 01:24:58,888
-哪？
-就在那儿，和买烟女说话的那个。
- Where?
- Right there. Talking to the cigarette girl.

1107
01:24:59,022 --> 01:25:01,809
那不是苏珊。我之前从没见过那个女孩。
That's not Susan.
I never even seen that girl before.

1108
01:25:01,942 --> 01:25:04,563
迪兹，那是苏珊。你认为我能搞错吗？
Dez, that's Susan.
Don't you think I should know?

1109
01:25:05,486 --> 01:25:08,903
那可能是苏珊，但不是我的苏珊。
That might be a Susan
but that's not my Susan.

1110
01:25:09,032 --> 01:25:12,614
-那是我的苏珊。
-那么在巴特利公园的女孩是谁？
- That's my Susan.
- Then who was the girl at Battery Park?

1111
01:25:25,675 --> 01:25:27,668
谁是陌生人？
So who's the stranger?

1112
01:25:27,803 --> 01:25:29,878
吉米！
Jimmy!

1113
01:25:30,013 --> 01:25:32,053
谁是陌生人？
Who's the stranger?

1114
01:25:32,182 --> 01:25:34,673
-说来话长。
-嗯啊。
- It's a long story.
- uh-huh.

1115
01:25:34,809 --> 01:25:36,933
你怎么也不会知道她的。
You wouldn't know her anyway.

1116
01:25:37,062 --> 01:25:39,101
-她？
-是，她。
- Her?
- Yeah. Her.

1117
01:25:41,858 --> 01:25:44,528
过来，找个私人空间去说话。
Come on. We'll talk about it in private.

1118
01:25:45,239 --> 01:25:47,277
敲门
(knocking)

1119
01:25:47,407 --> 01:25:50,028
我们还有三分钟上场。
We've got three minutes before curtain!

1120
01:25:50,159 --> 01:25:52,199
戴上你的假发马上出发。
Get your wig on and get out there!

1121
01:26:00,544 --> 01:26:02,537
我在想苏珊会不会出事。
I wonder what happened to Susan.

1122
01:26:02,672 --> 01:26:04,913
看起来像是你丢了女友。
Looks like you lost your girlfriend.

1123
01:26:05,049 --> 01:26:07,375
嘿，赖瑞，我结婚了，懂吗？
Hey, Larry! I'm married, all right?

1124
01:26:07,510 --> 01:26:09,798
-哦，得了吧。
-怎么？
- Oh, please!
- What?

1125
01:26:09,929 --> 01:26:11,969
乐队声
(band plays fanfare)

1126
01:26:15,727 --> 01:26:18,348
晚上好，女士们先生们。
Good evening, ladies and gentlemen.

1127
01:26:18,479 --> 01:26:21,765
欢迎来到魔术俱乐部，我是主持人，雷。
Welcome to the Magic Club.
I'm your host, Ray...

1128
01:26:23,318 --> 01:26:26,188
酒吧生，给我结帐吧。
Bartender...
Can I have the check, please?

1129
01:26:27,822 --> 01:26:30,692
有谁从女皇区出来的吗？
Hey, is there anyone out here
from, uh... Queens?

1130
01:26:30,825 --> 01:26:33,316
你。好的。我自己是从正常人家的肚子里出来的。
You. Well, I'm from
normal parents myself.

1131
01:26:33,452 --> 01:26:34,650
零星笑声
(scattered laughter)

1132
01:26:34,787 --> 01:26:39,199
是这样的，今晚我们给大家一个特别的待遇。
Anyway, we got a special treat
for you people this evening.

1133
01:26:39,333 --> 01:26:41,789
让我介绍一下独一无二的，举世无双的…
Introducing the one, the only...

1134
01:26:42,252 --> 01:26:44,292
苏珊，快上来。
Susan, get up here!

1135
01:26:44,422 --> 01:26:47,707
…还有他可爱的助手，Davina…
...and his very lovely assistant, Davina...

1136
01:26:47,841 --> 01:26:51,127
…今夜女王，鼓掌吧。
...Queen of the Night! So let's hear it!

1137
01:27:02,106 --> 01:27:05,309
加里，那是…
(Leslie) Gary... Is that...

1138
01:27:05,441 --> 01:27:07,933
不会吧。
It can't be.

1139
01:27:08,070 --> 01:27:10,905
我太喜欢了，真是好魔术啊。
I'm really enjoying this. It's a great trick.

1140
01:27:19,497 --> 01:27:21,289
苏珊？
Susan?

1141
01:27:21,416 --> 01:27:24,370
-罗伯塔？
-我不敢相信。
- Roberta?
- I don't believe it.

1142
01:27:25,127 --> 01:27:27,914
-罗伯塔…
-加里，坐下。
- Roberta...
- Gary, sit down.

1143
01:27:35,596 --> 01:27:38,087
呃，我在这儿呆会儿，谢谢。
uh... I think I'll be staying, thank you.

1144
01:27:38,223 --> 01:27:39,801
鼓
(drum roll)

1145
01:27:57,663 --> 01:28:00,580
烟，要烟吗？
Cigars? Cigarettes?

1146
01:28:02,793 --> 01:28:05,034
她还是很有型的啊。
She's really got style in a way.

1147
01:28:05,170 --> 01:28:07,210
她很不错啊，加里。
She's good, Gary.

1148
01:28:08,841 --> 01:28:10,880
哦，对不起。
(Larry) Right. Sorry.

1149
01:28:30,615 --> 01:28:32,653
尖叫
(Roberta screams)

1150
01:28:45,962 --> 01:28:48,002
(screams)

1151
01:28:50,550 --> 01:28:52,377
哇哦！
Bravo!

1152
01:28:57,182 --> 01:28:59,851
是他，就是他。
That's him. That's the guy.

1153
01:29:02,896 --> 01:29:03,975
就是他！
That's the guy!

1154
01:29:04,105 --> 01:29:05,897
嗨，救救我。
Hey, help me!

1155
01:29:06,482 --> 01:29:09,399
嘿，就是他，就是他，救命。
Hey! That's the guy!
That's the guy! Help!

1156
01:29:09,527 --> 01:29:13,145
来人抓住他，帮帮我。
Somebody stop that guy! Help!

1157
01:29:15,201 --> 01:29:17,324
怎么…罗伯塔。
What... Roberta!

1158
01:29:17,454 --> 01:29:19,861
-罗伯塔。
-你是谁？
- Roberta!
- Who are you?

1159
01:29:22,208 --> 01:29:24,247
怎么了？
What's going on?!

1160
01:29:29,715 --> 01:29:32,004
-他打伤你了？我杀了他。
-加里。
- Did he hurt you? I'll kill him!
- Gary!

1161
01:29:32,135 --> 01:29:35,170
-没事了，我现在可以搞定了。
-这人是谁？
- It's OK, I can take care of it now.
- Who is this guy?

1162
01:29:35,303 --> 01:29:37,343
你是谁？你什么意思，我是谁？
Who are you?
What do you mean, who am I?

1163
01:29:37,473 --> 01:29:39,300
-拜托…
-哦。
- Please...
- Oh.

1164
01:29:41,184 --> 01:29:43,592
加里，迪兹。
Gary... Dez.

1165
01:29:43,729 --> 01:29:46,398
迪兹，他是加里，我丈夫。
Dez, this is Gary, my husband.

1166
01:29:47,232 --> 01:29:49,059
嗨。
Hi.

1167
01:29:49,192 --> 01:29:52,193
-做热水盆的生意人？
-是。
- The hot-tub salesman?
- Yeah.

1168
01:29:52,321 --> 01:29:55,156
这么说你昨晚告诉我的是真的了。
So you were telling me
the truth last night.

1169
01:29:55,282 --> 01:29:57,321
昨晚？哦，不。
Last night? Oh, no.

1170
01:29:57,450 --> 01:29:59,776
-你和他过了一夜？
-加里…
- Did you spend the night with him?
- Gary...

1171
01:29:59,911 --> 01:30:02,782
-他就是警察提到的拉皮条的？
-他不是拉皮条的。
- Is he the pimp the police mentioned?
- He's not a pimp!

1172
01:30:02,914 --> 01:30:04,953
我不是拉皮条的，我是她一个朋友。
I'm not a pimp. I'm a friend of hers.

1173
01:30:05,083 --> 01:30:08,119
-有谁呢能告诉我发生什么了？
-我自己都不知道。
- Somebody tell me what's going on!
- I'm not sure myself.

1174
01:30:08,252 --> 01:30:10,292
-这段时间我糟糕透了…
-我也是。
- I'm having a hard time...
- So am I!

1175
01:30:10,421 --> 01:30:14,004
先停一停，停一停。
Wait a minute! Wait a minute!
Please, wait a minute, wait a minute.

1176
01:30:14,133 --> 01:30:15,544
听我说。
OK, listen.

1177
01:30:15,676 --> 01:30:20,588
迪兹，迪兹，我需要和加里单独谈一谈，好吗？
Dez. Dez, I really need to talk
to Gary alone, OK? Please?

1178
01:30:21,641 --> 01:30:23,183
好吧。
OK.

1179
01:30:23,309 --> 01:30:25,764
我也需要自己静一静。
I really need some time alone too.

1180
01:30:26,603 --> 01:30:28,643
对不起。
I'm sorry.

1181
01:30:35,656 --> 01:30:39,273
都过去了，没事了，噩梦结束了。
It's all right. It's all right.
The nightmare's over.

1182
01:30:40,745 --> 01:30:42,784
弹球机
(pinball machine pinging)

1183
